<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - Health Center</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
			background-image: url('/static/background.jpg'); /* Add background image */
            background-size: cover; /* Cover the entire viewport */
            background-position: center; /* Center the background image */
        }

         .navbar {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Increased transparency */
            padding: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar .logo img {
            height: 40px; /* Adjust the size as needed */
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: white; /* Change all links to white */
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem; /* Increased padding for larger link size */
            font-size: 1.3rem; /* Increased font size for better visibility */
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the text bold */
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s; /* Transition effect */
            border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded corners */
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); /* Light background on hover */
            color: #fff; /* White text on hover */
        }


        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h4 {
            color: #007BFF;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/static/ProjectLogo.jpeg" alt="Health Center Logo">
            <a href="#">Health Center</a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="http://localhost:5002/">Home</a>
			<a href="/healthbot" class="btn btn-light">Chat</a> <!-- Chat Option -->
            <a href="/about">About Us</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <h4>Contact Us</h4>
        <p>Have questions or need assistance? We're here to help!</p>

        <h4>Customer Support</h4>
        <p>Our dedicated customer support team is available to assist you with any inquiries or issues you may have. Whether it's a technical question, feedback, or a general inquiry, we're just a message away.</p>

        <h4>Get in Touch</h4>
        <p>Feel free to reach out to us via email or through the contact form below. We value your feedback and are committed to providing you with the best possible experience.</p>
        <p><b>Email:</b> suneelkumarparvathala@gmail.com</p>
        <p><b>Phone:</b> 9550558167</p>

        <h4>Stay Connected</h4>
        <p>Stay up-to-date with the latest news, updates, and health tips by following us on social media. Connect with us on Facebook or Instagram to join our growing community.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
